snippet.title: 100 Halloweens Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for 100 Halloweens, a third person survival horror game. Trapped in a mansion filled with 100 years of darkness... Fight or hide, stay alive and set things right.

Available now on Epic Game Store.

Music:
The Summoning by Scott Buckley | www.scottbuckley.com.au
Six cold feet in the ground | Leroy Carr

Ghostboxgames.com
